title: Community celebration: North Gate Fest is back
text: Community celebration: North Gate Fest is back Community celebration: North Gate Fest is back Photo by Beth Zagurski -- Emily Annabelle Koro answers questions at her jewelry booth at a past North Gate Music and Arts Fest. This year's 10th annual celebration starts at 4 p.m. Friday. Photo provided by The Easy -- The Easy is one of four local bands that will perform at North Gate Fest this October. Photo provided by Ship of Fools -- Ship of Fools -- Baton Rouge indie-rock and folk band Ship of Fools will perform at this year's North Gate Fest on Oct. 23. BY RANDEE ILES | Special to The Advocate Oct. 22, 2015; 4:57 p.m.
